title: No. 5 Red Raiders return with two days in Florida - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 5 Red Raiders return with two days in Florida - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: The No. 5-ranked Texas Tech men's golf team returns to competition next week at the Valspar Collegiate Invitational at the Floridian Golf Club in Palm City, Florida.
